{"tid":710181,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母點解中國旗會响人地場世界盃度出現?","createTime":"2018-06-20T14:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T08:12:21.000Z","uid":56701,"like":54,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3434b50d9a9ab59cd0a92e689bc6e8c5fe5a33f3","tid":710181,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:08:11.000Z","msg":"死撚開啦支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...你搞撚到我地華人好撚無面囉!<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好撚威呀...人地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">葡萄牙對摩洛哥</span>又關你乜撚嘢事呀?...做撚左<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第三世界國家呀?</span></span>...好撚柒威呀?弱智柒頭!<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母响世盃買得廣告多,霸左好多廣告位就係金主要去<em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">耀武揚威</span></span></em>,要响人地場波刷存在感呀?<br />\n<br />\n入到圍咩?屌你老母真柒到全世界華人都無晒面,就係啲低賤支那賊種搞出嚟...<br />\n<br />\n仲有岩岩人地日本嬴波又關你尻事...食屎啦死支賊! <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鬼唔望你下一介入到世界盃<br />\n</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後俾同組啲國家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 輪姦呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div></span></span>"},{"pid":"de3c75b1695717c254fe94f5c900d85e134c61d6","tid":710181,"uid":2263,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"好un眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ebe811abbdec8e249ed4941b91b654404e021d","tid":710181,"uid":56701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:14:42.000Z","msg":"推..."},{"pid":"997032dfb36e6d27f4e15d38a062d203eff47451","tid":710181,"uid":141879,"like":1,"dislike":30,"score":-29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:19:58.000Z","msg":"雖然中國係球場裏面冇咩角色，但係球場外其他位置都搵到佢既蹤影，例如裁判團隊、廣告賺助、供應商，所以球場上有國旗都好正常"},{"pid":"d02467aff2446523b0d45300f8f536cce96703cd","tid":710181,"uid":56701,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"997032dfb36e6d27f4e15d38a062d203eff47451","tid":710181,"uid":141879,"like":1,"dislike":30,"score":-29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:19:58.000Z","msg":"雖然中國係球場裏面冇咩角色，但係球場外其他位置都搵到佢既蹤影，例如裁判團隊、廣告賺助、供應商，所以球場上有國旗都好正常"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:35:39.000Z","msg":"係呀係呀..個波同個獎盃仲有啲波衫都係中國制呀...連食飯果啲刀叉碗碟都係呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁關人地場波乜事呀!...屌佢老母!成件事好撚柒呀!你明唔明呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"850737cc66aff62367c4e76824b420a2fc8db886","tid":710181,"uid":60524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"圖都唔比張 你話你縮係老母入面都有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c2ded27536c06902a254c527a88cfe3cb6b2b7","tid":710181,"uid":48074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:44:00.000Z","msg":"樓主唔好強人所難啦<br />\n中國咁閪廢好難入決賽周嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1aef5563937016ebb82c62dbad3637879cdba73","tid":710181,"uid":44807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"850737cc66aff62367c4e76824b420a2fc8db886","tid":710181,"uid":60524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"圖都唔比張 你話你縮係老母入面都有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙龍門後面啊，我都見到<br />\n睇下場波先好串人啦"},{"pid":"3624bec49de6194278b39bfbc514c8b68c10bd30","tid":710181,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:45:08.000Z","